s chapter provides a comprehensive exploration of the topic, covering its definition, historical context, methods employed by thieves, personal information at risk, impacts on individuals and society, prevention and protection strategies, detection and response measures, future trends, and real-life examples. It offers readers a thorough understanding of identity theft, equipping them with the knowledge necessary to safeguard their personal information and mitigate the risks associated with this pervasive and evolving threat in the digital age.},
